 victor hugo 
 
 
 


 
 the empire strikes back 
 xi 
 
 it was dawn on the gaseous bespin planet 
 as the millennium falcon began its approach through the atmosphere itsoared past several of many moons the planet itself glowed with the samesoft pink hue of dawn that tinted the hull of the powerful pirate starship as the shipneared it swerved to avoid a billowing canyon of clouds that swirled up around theplanet 
