 the wind buffeted the little cottage and the fire leapt and crackled and bill was soon opening another bottle of wine lupins news seemed to have taken them out of themselves removed them for a while from their state of siege tidings of new life were exhilarating only the goblin seemed untouched by the suddenly festive atmosphere and after a while he slunk back to the bedroom he now occupied alone harry thought he was the only one who had noticed this until he saw bills eyes following the goblin up the stairs 
 
