 some of the hogmen their hands protected by thick black gloves approached body of han solo and shoved the block over after the figure crashedto the platform with a loud metallic clang the ugnaughts hoisted it into container they then attached a boxlike electronic device to its sideand stepped away 
 kneeling lando turned some knobs on the device and checked the gaugemeasuring the temperature of body he sighed with relief and nodded hishead alive he informed han anxious friends and in perfecthibernation 
