 just landed my lord an aide informed him 
 see to it that he finds his way here 
 indicating leia and chewbacca lando told vader take what is mine was determined to whisk them out of clutches before the dark lordreneged on their contract 
 take them vader said but keeping a detachment of troops here to watchover them 
