 well never get out its too big hermione screamed but the dragon opened its mouth and belched flame again blasting the tunnel whose floors and ceiling cracked and crumbled by sheer force the dragon clawed and fought its way through harrys eyes were shut tight against the heat and dust deafened by the crash of rock and the dragons roars he could only cling to its back expecting to be shaken off at any moment then he heard hermione yelling defodio 
 
