 the empire strikes back 
 xiii 
 
 six imperial stormtroopers guarded lando leia and chewbacca as they marchedthrough the inner corridor of cloud city they reached an intersection when twelveof guards and his aide arrived to block their path 
 code force seven lando commanded as he stopped in front of his aide 
 at that moment the twelve guards aimed their laser weapons at the startledstormtroopers and aide calmly took the six troopers weapons from handed one of the guns to leia and one to lando then waited for the next order 
 hold them in the security tower the cloud city administrator said one must know 
 the guards and aide carrying the extra weapons marched thestormtroopers away to the tower 
 leia had watched this rapid turn of events in confusion but her confusionturned to astonishment when lando the man who had betrayed han solo beganremoving bonds 
 come on he urged getting out of here 
 the giant hands were freed at last not caring to wait forexplanations chewbacca turned toward the man who had freed him and with roar lunged at lando and began to throttle him 
 after what you did to han leia said i trust you to 
 lando desperately trying to free himself from ferocious grip triedto explain i had no choice he the wookiee interrupted him with anangry bark 
 still a chance to save han lando gasped at the eastplatform 
 chewie leia said at last go 
 still fuming chewbacca released lando and glared at him as calrissian foughtto regain his breath 
 keep your eyes on him chewie leia cautioned as the wookiee growledthreateningly 
 i have a feeling lando muttered under his breath that making anotherbig mistake 
 the stout little r unit meandered up and down the corridor sending hisscanners in every possible direction as he tried to detect some sign of his any kind of life he realized he was dreadfully turned around and had lost trackof how many meters he had traveled 
 as turned a corner he spotted a number of forms moving up thecorridor beeping and whistling droid greetings he hoped that these were friendlysorts 
 his tooting was detected by one of the creatures who began to call out to him 
 artooartoo it was threepio 
 chewbacca still carrying the semiassembled quickly turnedaround to see the stubby r droid rolling their way but as the wookiee was spun out of sight of his friend 
 wait the aggravated threepio demanded turn around you trying to save han from the bounty hunter 
 artoo scooted forward beeping all the way and threepio patiently replied to hisfrantic questions 
 i know but master luke can take care of himself at least that was kept telling himself as the group continued its search for han 
 on the east landing platform of cloud city two guards shoved the frozen bodyof han solo through a side hatchway of the slave boba fett climbed up a laddernext to the opening and boarded his ship ordering it sealed as soon as he entered thecockpit 
 fett ignited his engines and the craft began rolling across the platform fortakeoff 
 lando leia and chewbacca raced onto the platform in time only to see theslave lifting off and soaring into the orange and purple of the cloud city his blaster chewbacca howled and fired the weapon at the departingspaceship 
 no use lando told him out of range 
